title: Nest CO Alarm: Status
agents: nest
catalog: hw/enviroment
license: GPL
distribution: adams_consuting_github
description:
 This check monitors the reported CO status of the Nest CO Alarm
 to the central Nest service.
 The {Access Token} in the Wato {Host & Services Parameters} is required
 for the agent to query the Nest API.

item:
 The operational status of the Nest CO Alarm.

inventory:
 One check for each registered CO Alarm is created by the inventory

[parameters]
parameters (none): No parameters are required for this check

[configuration]
nest_co_default (none): No values are requred for this check

